  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Goals</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the last remaining commander.Develop your sector over 50 days and defend it from invading alien spaceships. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Play</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607310/extras/b1dd068115d3aa2611205f490338557e.poster.avif?t=1754966590\" width=300 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607310/extras/b1dd068115d3aa2611205f490338557e.webm?t=1754966590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607310/extras/b1dd068115d3aa2611205f490338557e.mp4?t=1754966590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Construct buildings on hexagon-shaped terrain tiles.There are combinations that create synergy between each building.Use synergy/terrain to build the best combination. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607310/extras/c67dc9326239c22828bd17adf34fc934.poster.avif?t=1754966590\" width=300 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607310/extras/c67dc9326239c22828bd17adf34fc934.webm?t=1754966590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607310/extras/c67dc9326239c22828bd17adf34fc934.mp4?t=1754966590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>17 battles occur over 50 days.Defend all 17 battles to win the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Management</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607310/extras/56b772e0b6c43616b1da70a8becc22f5.poster.avif?t=1754966590\" width=300 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607310/extras/56b772e0b6c43616b1da70a8becc22f5.webm?t=1754966590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607310/extras/56b772e0b6c43616b1da70a8becc22f5.mp4?t=1754966590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Evaluation resources for hope/administration/education exist.Manage your evaluation resources by managing complaints.</p>",
